Larry J. Pollock's Biography




			Larry J. Pollock has been Executive Vice President, Chief Manufacturing Officer since May 2015.  Mr. Pollock served as Director of Tube Manufacturing at TimkenSteel prior to joining the Company and General Manager at The Timken Company from 2010 through 2014.  Prior to joining Timken, Mr. Pollock was the General Manager at SPS Technologies/PCC where he was responsible for the aerospace fasteners business unit.  From 1987 to 2009, Mr. Pollock held several positions at Pilkington/Nippon Sheet Glass Company.
		
Source: Universal Stainless & Alloy Products, Inc. on 02/22/2017
		
	

 






